<div class="hero-section">
    <img src="/images/profile.webp" alt="Pranav" class="profile-pic" loading="lazy">
    <h2>Hell<span class="o o1">o</span><span class="o o2">o</span><span class="o o3">o</span><span class="o o4">o</span><span class="o o5">o</span><span class="o o6">o</span><span class="o o7">o</span><span class="o o8">o</span><span class="o o9">o</span><span class="o o10">o</span><span class="o o11">o</span><span class="o o12">o</span><span class="o o13">o</span><span class="o o14">o</span><span class="o o15">o</span><span class="o o16">o</span><span class="o o17">o</span><span class="o o18">o</span><span class="o o19">o</span><span class="o o20">o</span><span class="o o21">o</span><span class="o o22">o</span><span class="o o23">o</span></h2>
    <script>!function(){var h=document.querySelector('.hero-section h2');if(!h)return;var s=67;h.style.fontSize=s+'px';while(h.scrollWidth>h.clientWidth&&s>24)h.style.fontSize=--s+'px';h.style.visibility='visible'}()</script>
</div>

<p class="intro">
    I'm Pranav, a newly minted graduate of the <em>University of Virginia</em> working for a <em>macro hedge fund</em> based in <em>NYC</em>
</p>

